該會對你把聲既悅耳程度有唔少改善"},{"pid":"6cb3ad36edefd3978ecef0f2419777a6a465fed0","tid":276912,"uid":104217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"D人成日話我講野冇高低音 好似就斷氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我唔係好瘦弱個d人 我都唔會聽返自己錄音 把聲咁我都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 言語治療有冇用"},{"pid":"bcaf7ad89e5aebe62df7113d720f84b7956aab48","tid":276912,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D人成日話我講野冇高低音 好似就斷氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我唔係好瘦弱個d人 我都唔會聽返自己錄音 把聲咁我都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 言語治療有冇用</blockquote><br />\n你自己對鏡講多d好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗乜去到言語治療"}]}